{"tid":367670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲有人會FF香港可以有民主🤦🏻‍♂️","createTime":"2017-08-21T02:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T07:08:39.000Z","uid":82929,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdfb459cb0072fc6b0dbcb193fa160fe9413c264","tid":367670,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"參考下台灣、南泡點變革<br />\n人地既示威<br />\n再比較一下背後既美國、同支共<br />\n<br />\n香港反對派真係好幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每年71、64搞大遊行、大集會，咁撚熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸撚哂天時<br />\n每次遊行都係得一個起點、終點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想玩下包圍、做下衝突點都做唔到。衝突點都冇又點樣引爆群眾心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇一次成功包圍到一個高官、法官、立法會議員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，發夢個陣去過反國教、反東北、10月1意圖圍會展<br />\n已經坐到屎忽爛、企到腳都軟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa305ea0784bdbc270dd44e59a0085a939a6540","tid":367670,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"再進一步就去到死人"},{"pid":"17d60d376d99a97ddba2681488cb7eff957055b4","tid":367670,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"唔武力，唔獨立，無可能有民主<br />\n<br />\n不過對好多人嚟講，民主唔可以當飯食，都係做順民"},{"pid":"a3d4d319db17d530d295720cf62ce85227151602","tid":367670,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔武力，唔獨立，無可能有民主<br />\n<br />\n不過對好多人嚟講，民主唔可以當飯食，都係做順民</blockquote><br />\n晚晚老蘭都塞爆人瘋狂隊酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個星期日入西貢船P都塞滿人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真正歌舞昇平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歷史上有冇人會係歌舞昇平下搞革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登聖地黃